{
  "text": "Any public service, rather than being a response to market shortcomings or to a natural monopoly, must offer added value, which should be assessed and monitored [CITATION_1] . And that added value is linked to the strengthening of the audience as citizenry (Jacubowicz, 2009 ) and the empowerment of society (EBU, 2012) .",
